{"tid":2230747,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台前將領：勝負取決制空權","createTime":"2020-10-05T06:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:26:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36a414ec178de77f6c1323bf2992b88d233d4047","tid":2230747,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201005/IF6GTTKSTRAZ5DMHAS2J4DJHNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201005%2FIF6GTTKSTRAZ5DMHAS2J4DJHNI%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGKy4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=77b09b78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201005%2FIF6GTTKSTRAZ5DMHAS2J4DJHNI%2F&h=36ac7343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201005/IF6GTTKSTRAZ5DMHAS2J4DJHNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台前將領：勝負取決制空權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S4mhX_bkrYfI5szDo-0a-RJMpu0=/814x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DQYH6U45JNHEHPXRLKR6XY27LQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS4mhX_bkrYfI5szDo-0a-RJMpu0%3D%2F814x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDQYH6U45JNHEHPXRLKR6XY27LQ.jpg&h=1f5d4eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■共機「運-8」入侵台灣西南空域遭驅離。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍頻頻擾台，兩岸局勢日益緊張。台灣前總統馬英九稱「首戰即終戰」，讓人憂心。台軍空軍前副司令張延廷向《台蘋》表示，只要台軍戰術得宜，還是可能變持久戰，不會只打幾天就結束，加上各國對大陸虎視眈眈，美軍也可能協防台灣，「中國一旦冒險開戰，反而可能兵敗如山倒。」<br />\n<br />\n「馬英九不是唱衰，是善意的提醒，共軍與國軍的預算差距高達15倍，但國軍的戰力也不是不堪一擊。」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解放軍軍機多次闖台空域<br />\n<br />\n張延廷認為勝負取決於哪方掌握制空權。他指：「如果國軍戰法得當，用對佈署，兩岸戰爭是可以變成持久戰，不會只有撐三天、五天。加上其他各國都虎視眈眈，可能趁亂也與中國開戰，國際也可能介入協防台灣，中國一旦冒險開戰，反而可能兵敗如山倒，若內部局勢又不穩，甚至可能危及中共政權。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，台灣軍方表示，解放軍「運-8」反潛機昨午進入台灣西南的防空識別區。台軍戰機升空驅離，並用防空導彈追蹤監控。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網 / 台灣國防部"},{"pid":"5b50d76448667ebe35ee591cd0bcc7e1e308fb88","tid":2230747,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"廢話"},{"pid":"90e18cf917266d80ab52b1ec501c05d8fc80392c","tid":2230747,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"阿媽係男人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c326e79d5ffc0c84d40a0889086092db1bab085b","tid":2230747,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90e18cf917266d80ab52b1ec501c05d8fc80392c","tid":2230747,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"阿媽係男人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"全港最大嘅同性戀論壇，連台海戰爭都gay不可失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91dd14c27773f246f966060165ec84296016041","tid":2230747,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"支那同台灣邊個贏面高d"},{"pid":"97239997c1cf8f132d8158d4181e13fac4fad032","tid":2230747,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"no shit"},{"pid":"cddc3486c387b9f6c37608d909a89e47d7f613c2","tid":2230747,"uid":269498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"台灣策略<br />\n偵察：PAWS+美日情報<br />\n海上攔截：艦隊+無人機群+水雷<br />\n防空：天弓+愛國者+復仇者+F16V+E2D+P3C<br />\n反登陸：M1A2+M109+CM32<br />\n步兵團：標槍+刺針+無人機脈衝炮<br />\n反浸透：內政部+憲兵隊<br />\n反擊：萬劍+雲峰+MK48"}]}